<div class='communityQuestionSubTitle'>
Popular Answered Questions
</div>
<div id='communityQuestionsWithAnswers'>
<div class='communityQuestionAndAnswer'>
<div class='communityQuestion'>
<div class='questionText'>
<a href="/questions/1464279-i-keep-wondering-why-this-series-hasn-t">I keep wondering why this series hasn&#39;t been made into a movie, TV series or mini series. Surely we have the CGI technology.
Has this series been forgotten? I am currently rereading it and recommending it to my grandsons.

I like the tone of the stories in that the plots revolve around overcoming hardships and adversity. The characters are pretty well fleshed out and you can see them in your mind&#39;s eye.</a>
</div>
<div class='communityQAFooter questionFooter'>
<ul class='questionFooterActions'>
<li class='footerItem like'>
<span class='likeItContainer' id='like_container_community_question_1464279'><a id="like_count_community_question_1464279" rel="nofollow" href="/rating/voters/1464279?resource_type=CommunityQuestion"><span class="likesCount">3 likes</span></a>&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;<a rel="nofollow" class="jsLike like_it" href="https://www.goodreads.com/user/new?remember=true&amp;return_url=%2Fbook%2Fshow%2F61942.The_Dragonriders_of_Pern">like</a></span>

</li>
<li class='footerItem communityQuestionTimestamp'>
<a href="/questions/1464279-i-keep-wondering-why-this-series-hasn-t">2 years ago</a>
</li>
