<div id="review_2806806135" class="review" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/2806806135" />
    <a title="Crimson Sparrow" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/29050563-crimson-sparrow"><img alt="Crimson Sparrow" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1393359477p2/29050563.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/2806806135?book_show_action=true">May 02, 2019</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Crimson Sparrow" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Crimson Sparrow" href="/user/show/29050563-crimson-sparrow">Crimson Sparrow</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="really liked it"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">really liked it</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span></span>



        

    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer2806806135" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer11228854803297510395">I LOVED these books as a teen. They captivated me and made me fall in love with dragons - an obsession I maintain to this day. If I had rated them then, it would have been 5 stars: A strong-willed, resourceful female lead marked for greatness, telepathy, animals, a brilliant blend of science and fantasy - what&apos;s not to love?<br/><br/>I don&apos;t know that the stories have aged well, but they shaped me. I owe so much of my love of fantasy and sci fi to these books, and regardless of their current appeal, McCaf</span>
  <span id="freeText11228854803297510395" style="display:none">I LOVED these books as a teen. They captivated me and made me fall in love with dragons - an obsession I maintain to this day. If I had rated them then, it would have been 5 stars: A strong-willed, resourceful female lead marked for greatness, telepathy, animals, a brilliant blend of science and fantasy - what's not to love?<br /><br />I don't know that the stories have aged well, but they shaped me. I owe so much of my love of fantasy and sci fi to these books, and regardless of their current appeal, McCaffrey knows how to weave a seamless and realistic tale.</span>
  <a data-text-id="11228854803297510395" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

          </span>
        </div>


