    <div class="section">
      

<div id="review_2477661886" class="review" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/2477661886" />
    <a title="Susan" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/3218791-susan"><img alt="Susan" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1442620428p2/3218791.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/2477661886?book_show_action=true">Nov 11, 2018</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Susan" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Susan" href="/user/show/3218791-susan">Susan</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="liked it"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">liked it</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span></span>

          <span class="greyText">&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;</span>
          <a class="lightGreyText" title="Kindle Edition " href="/book/show/8356426-the-dragonriders-of-pern">review of another edition</a>


        

    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer2477661886" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer2653459483520070492">Went back to read this in a fit of nostalgia, and realized I should have left well enough alone. I still love the original concept, but the original characters, not so much. Especially Lessa. Now that I&apos;m older, her manipulative interactions grate. Ah, well, I&apos;ll remember the dragons happily, and keep it at that.</span>
  <span id="freeText2653459483520070492" style="display:none">Went back to read this in a fit of nostalgia, and realized I should have left well enough alone. I still love the original concept, but the original characters, not so much. Especially Lessa. Now that I'm older, her manipulative interactions grate. Ah, well, I'll remember the dragons happily, and keep it at that.</span>
  <a data-text-id="2653459483520070492" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

