<a href="https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/44660.The_Belgariad_Boxed_Set"><img alt="The Belgariad Boxed Set: Pawn of Prophecy / Queen of Sorcery / Magician&#39;s Gambit / Castle of Wizardry / Enchanters&#39; End Game (The Belgariad, #1-5)" src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/books/1391347386l/44660._SX98_.jpg" />
